        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aditya-aryam-59b188202"><i class="footicon fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
        <p style="font-size: 12px;"> <i class="far fa-copyright"></i> 2021-2022 Aditya Aryam. All Rights Reserved</p> 

    </section>
    
</body>
</html> 